Subject: Remote Device Management / Remote wiping capability
Description:
USB storage devices that are encrypted using EasyLock, EasyLock together with all documents encrypted inside can be removed/ deleted by using the "Reset Device" button; files stored outside EasyLock are not removed/ deleted.  

But when we tested in real time scenario. We have found that data present before encryption as well.
